gerundet.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access. Unless otherwise specified individually in the content, the work is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives (CC BY-NC-ND) license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/3.0 uhttp://www.transcript-verlag.de/open-access-bei-transcript  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mrz 2021) 0aOccupationsxSociological aspects. 0aProfessionsxSociological aspects. 4aArbeit. 4aArbeits- und Industriesoziologie. 4aArbeitslosigkeit. 4aEinführung. 4aModerne Gesellschaft. 4aProfession. 4aSoziologie. 4aWirtschaftssoziologie. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aEconomic Sociology.  aIntroduction.  aSociology of Work and Industry.  aSociology.40uhttps://doi.org/10.14361/9783839400500zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839400500zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783839400500.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GOA